  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to libnftnl</title>

    <para>
      The <application>libnftnl</application> library provides a low-level
      netlink programming interface (API) to the in-kernel nf_tables subsystem.
    </para>

    &lfs90_checked;

